{"TopicId":71316,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Fairings without mods","CreatedByName":"The Jeb.","CreatedById":104516,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-05-03T16:37:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Jeb.","CreatedById":104516,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-05-03T16:37:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHello, today i will show you how to make fairings without mods! Tip: use L(left)SHIFT \u002B W,A,S,D to rotate or move in degrees a part! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPros:\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFFFFF;\u0022\u003E908776556777677666766765665666566655566666\u003C/span\u003E Cons:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-Use as heatshield\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-More chances to protect your ship in impact \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFFFFF;\u0022\u003E000000000000\u003C/span\u003E -Looks uglier\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-Replaces Procedural Fairings and get some RAM memory\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-No mods needed\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWARNING!: watch closely to the part to know how to make it!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELet\u0027s get started:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E1. Get a pod from parts menu(everything you want)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Yqskewz.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Yqskewz.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E2. Put a decoupler\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/RijcxUH.png\u0022 alt=\u0022RijcxUH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E3. Put another 6 radial decouplers (how much is needed to make the fairing cover all spacecraft and you can put it horizontal or vertical)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LNnjDMH.png\u0022 alt=\u0022LNnjDMH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E4. Put first part of fairings(and you can put extensions under it)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/5ZXbFCV.png\u0022 alt=\u00225ZXbFCV.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bBkStRY.png\u0022 alt=\u0022bBkStRY.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E5. Put the second part of fairings( use SHIFT\u002B W,A,S,D to make it how you want and look better)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0BMEbqu.png\u0022 alt=\u00220BMEbqu.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xkwAzhZ.png\u0022 alt=\u0022xkwAzhZ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E6. Ready to test!( I used cheats to put it in SPACE to do this fasterr!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/rWRiPqI.png\u0022 alt=\u0022rWRiPqI.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/moDQOOe.png\u0022 alt=\u0022moDQOOe.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E7. DECOUPLE!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/8JXWVFr.png\u0022 alt=\u00228JXWVFr.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E7,5. Decouple the normal decoupler to dissapear that things after decoupling fairing\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/7XpyVG9.png\u0022 alt=\u00227XpyVG9.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#00FF00;\u0022\u003ETEST COMPLETE\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EAnd about extensions:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/EGY4Dc1.png\u0022 alt=\u0022EGY4Dc1.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003EDownload for the Command pod mk-1 fairing subassembly: \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www./view/0vgj22g4rj5uqy8/mk1pod_fairing.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003Ehttp://www./view/0vgj22g4rj5uqy8/mk1pod_fairing.craft\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-05-04T12:50:26Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2014 12:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by The Jeb.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}